       ,convert(varchar(10)
       ,cast(a.UltimaAsistida as date), 101)  UltimaAsistida
       ,a.observacion
       ,a.fallecido 
       FROM 
       VIEW_repconsultas4 a 
       Where 
        a.fecha_cita  between '11/15/2019' and '11/15/2019' and a.activa<>'0' and a.asistido<>3  and a.usuario='KBLASINI'  and a.fallecido<>'1'  order by a.fecha_cita desc, a.nombres OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 25  ROWS ONLY
